                            <comment id="13053229" author="dejanb" created="Wed, 22 Jun 2011 12:58:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This should now be fixed with svn revision 1138443&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Default size of the transaction that will be kept in the memory is 10MB. This can be tuned with &lt;tt&gt;maxKahaDBTxSize&lt;/tt&gt; system property (in bytes)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13176156" author="dejanb" created="Tue, 27 Dec 2011 12:31:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Additional fix in svn revision 1224890&lt;/p&gt;

